{"tid":2361973,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"黑子的籃球入面綠間嗰隊根本就係笑話嚟","createTime":"2021-01-11T06:22:42.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-11T07:33:13.000Z","uid":370062,"like":0,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"05b94c56573b48d68f74b5a62c38077be4279634","tid":2361973,"uid":370062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T06:22:42.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/7D1hd6RlSuo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F7D1hd6RlSuo&d=7oH93WZedTbABA3XB48d7WLZ6li1RkmcNQmTobTGNbY%3D&h=9060ff65\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/7D1hd6RlSuo</a><br />\n大家可以睇咗呢條片先<br />\n兩分半鐘好快睇曬<br />\n講翻黑子的籃球<br />\n其實只要綠間嗰隊球球都用砲台山戰術<br />\n根本就冇人阻止到綠間入波<br />\n咁你可能會問防守點算<br />\n我諗到一招<br />\n就係喺三分線外用one on one戰術<br />\n完全唔畀機會對面射三分波<br />\n然後只要對手一入三分線就唔守佢<br />\n你唔守佢冇理由唔攞分掛<br />\n咁樣一來一往<br />\n你3分佢2分<br />\n根本冇可能會輸<br />\n又或者簡單啲<br />\n綠間一射完三分波即刻用罩波戰術用到完場<br />\n有乜理由會輸到<br />\n所以其實佢嗰隊根本就係笑話嚟"},{"pid":"d917bb08908802f24f1d3a0729d74f02a9f58f0c","tid":2361973,"uid":54579,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T06:24:50.000Z","msg":"你阿媽個波罩你阿"},{"pid":"d03fa2526967ce9abd22fdc7cbd4c82bdd854853","tid":2361973,"uid":192465,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T06:29:01.000Z","msg":"有咩on9得過睇黑子籃球<br />\n<br />\n就係認真睇黑子籃球<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f277d609ab77f4cbd63ab506eace667a3170487","tid":2361973,"uid":370062,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"d03fa2526967ce9abd22fdc7cbd4c82bdd854853","tid":2361973,"uid":192465,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T06:29:01.000Z","msg":"有咩on9得過睇黑子籃球<br />\n<br />\n就係認真睇黑子籃球<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T06:31:04.000Z","msg":"我不嬲都好認真咁對待每件事<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"861ca5925c625c86ac7ef60289529d44e9bb445f","tid":2361973,"uid":90515